main event: Observers in Dexter, Ohio reported seeing two gold-white glowing objects in the sky for about ten minutes.
interesting points: The objects were observed several times on 5-6 June around the same time of day., Objects increased speed and altitude before disappearing from sight., No sound was heard during the sighting., The objects' descriptions matched landing lights, anti-collision lights, and wing/tail lights of aircraft., Military aircraft were present in the area at the time of the sighting.
sighted object: two gold-white glowing objects in the sky
witness description: Observers who noted the luminous objects
